00:45:49,081 --> 00:45:51,208
It pricks, it stings;

517
00:45:51,416 --> 00:45:53,646
it's a welcome offence.

518
00:45:53,852 --> 00:45:56,013
I seek its lap

519
00:45:56,221 --> 00:46:00,885
to end my day...

520
00:46:01,093 --> 00:46:03,323
...I join its embrace

521
00:46:03,529 --> 00:46:07,659
to veil my dismay.

522
00:46:08,400 --> 00:46:13,099
Like my black renegade kohl,

523
00:46:13,305 --> 00:46:17,799
it streams down my face.

524
00:46:20,045 --> 00:46:25,073
The moon's mate, o' night,
you come to me forlorn.

525
00:46:25,284 --> 00:46:29,846
Where is your friend,
the elusive moon,

526
00:46:30,055 --> 00:46:33,752
why do you come alone?

527
00:46:36,828 --> 00:46:39,388
Extinguish the twilight,

528
00:46:39,598 --> 00:46:41,725
eclipse the dark...

529
00:46:41,934 --> 00:46:46,598
...I only wish to speak

530
00:46:46,805 --> 00:46:50,434
to the pitch in the black.

531
00:46:53,178 --> 00:47:00,016
The night is sad...

532
00:47:00,452 --> 00:47:10,123
...it's heavy with grief...
- Let's go, Lolita.

533
00:47:12,297 --> 00:47:15,698
...sitting in its own dark shadow.

534
00:48:09,788 --> 00:48:11,085
Not a musician...

535
00:48:15,661 --> 00:48:17,094
Just a businessman.

536
00:48:19,698 --> 00:48:20,858
Uncle Raghu...

537
00:48:26,972 --> 00:48:29,907
Son. - Yes, mother.

538
00:48:30,976 --> 00:48:34,844
Some bad news...
Mr. Gurucharan is no more.

539
00:48:39,284 --> 00:48:43,618
The wedding happened quickly
to fulfill his last wish.

540
00:48:46,458 --> 00:48:47,550
Is it over?

541
00:48:49,461 --> 00:48:52,862
Yes. Girish managed everything.

542
00:48:55,334 --> 00:49:00,101
They'll be here next week
for the last rites.

543
00:52:32,517 --> 00:52:33,677
What's happening to you, son?

544
00:52:33,952 --> 00:52:35,419
Is everything okay?

545
00:52:37,188 --> 00:52:42,592
Tell Mr. Tantiya I'm ready to
marry his daughter Gayatri.

546
00:52:43,094 --> 00:52:48,726
Wonderful, son. I'll call them
first thing tomorrow morning.

547
00:52:49,868 --> 00:52:51,062
Come on, Rajeshwari.

548
00:53:26,638 --> 00:53:28,765
Have you composed this?

549
00:53:29,240 --> 00:53:32,767
No. It's Tagore's, stupid.

550
00:54:09,481 --> 00:54:13,645
Hello, Shekhar. Congratulations.

551
00:54:18,289 --> 00:54:19,950
Here to just congratulate me?

552
00:54:20,525 --> 00:54:25,929
I'm also here to give you
a parcel from Lolita.

553
00:54:28,033 --> 00:54:29,022
What's this?

554
00:54:30,702 --> 00:54:33,034
The papers to their house.

555
00:54:34,572 --> 00:54:35,698
Why are you giving it to me?

556
00:54:36,841 --> 00:54:38,274
Consider it your wedding gift.

557
00:54:41,146 --> 00:54:44,673
Tell her I don't want her charity.

558
00:54:45,884 --> 00:54:48,876
Not charity - a debt.

559
00:54:50,288 --> 00:54:55,225
She said she'll never be able
to pay you back completely.

560
00:54:56,327 --> 00:54:57,487
...but she's trying.

561
00:54:58,730 --> 00:55:00,698
Your wife's become pretty smart.

562
00:55:02,233 --> 00:55:11,835
Yes. And I really love her.

563
00:55:22,020 --> 00:55:24,045
Isn't this the tune you two sang?

564
00:55:25,256 --> 00:55:27,156
Day and night.

565
00:55:28,760 --> 00:55:32,355
It made me insanely jealous

566
00:55:33,531 --> 00:55:35,931
as to how someone
could love so much.

567
00:55:37,268 --> 00:55:41,568
But marriage cured me.

568
00:55:43,041 --> 00:55:50,243
My clever wife cured me my Koel.

569
00:55:51,216 --> 00:55:51,910
Koel?

570
00:55:54,119 --> 00:55:58,453
I know what you're thinking,
and rightly so.

571
00:55:59,858 --> 00:56:05,490
I loved Lolita very much...
but when I proposed to her

572
00:56:09,134 --> 00:56:11,068
...she said she was already married.

573
00:56:11,736 --> 00:56:15,502
I asked her but she didn't tell
me her husband's name.

574
00:56:16,374 --> 00:56:24,076
...But she never so miserable
...not even to Koel.

575
00:56:26,751 --> 00:56:31,654
But when she gave you
the house, I knew.

576
00:56:33,324 --> 00:56:37,192
The money you had given her
turned into a debt the day you...

577
00:56:37,395 --> 00:56:39,556
...decided to marry Gayatri.

578
00:56:41,866 --> 00:56:47,736
This debt will become a burden for her.
And she won't bear this burden...

579
00:56:48,940 --> 00:56:50,965
A burden she wasn't willing to carry.
That's who she is.

580
00:56:53,611 --> 00:57:00,414
I wanted to find that foolish man
and drag him to her feet.

581
00:57:02,020 --> 00:57:10,450
But you... you're not even worthy
of her feet. I pity you, Shekhar.

582
00:57:11,563 --> 00:57:13,997
You lost what was already yours.

583
00:57:15,400 --> 00:57:19,063
You're the most unfortunate soul
in the world.

584
00:57:23,074 --> 00:57:26,771
When are you all leaving?
- Right now.

585
00:57:29,047 --> 00:57:33,347
What have I done?
What do I do...?

586
00:57:34,285 --> 00:57:35,081
Shekhar.

587
00:57:41,860 --> 00:57:43,725
Ask daddy dearest.

588
00:57:56,574 --> 00:57:57,939
Why was Girish here?

589
00:58:08,019 --> 00:58:08,781
What is this?

590
00:58:16,928 --> 00:58:24,300
The papers of the house.

591
00:58:26,004 --> 00:58:32,705
He was here to make this deal?
How much does he want?

592
00:58:33,778 --> 00:58:39,910
Mr. Tantiya will be delighted.
Hello? Mr. Tantiya, please?

593
00:58:40,451 --> 00:58:43,011
Good news, Mr. Tantiya...

594
00:58:43,288 --> 00:58:45,984
we've got the house.

595
00:58:47,692 --> 00:58:49,819
We're just leaving for your house.

596
00:58:51,362 --> 00:58:57,062
My son has accomplished
what I couldn't.

597
00:58:57,902 --> 00:59:02,498
Behold. Mr. Gurucharan's house papers.

598
00:59:02,874 --> 00:59:06,537
Thank God, it's yours now.

599
00:59:07,879 --> 00:59:11,110
Or else God knows how many more
lives would've been destroyed.

600
00:59:11,649 --> 00:59:16,484
The house that killed Mr. Gurucharan
got Lolita...

601
00:59:16,688 --> 00:59:22,126
...fired with such indignity created
a wall between two families...

602
00:59:22,327 --> 00:59:23,453
Rajeshwari. Be quiet.

603
00:59:24,395 --> 00:59:27,262
Thank God, it's yours now.

604
00:59:27,465 --> 00:59:28,796
What is so wrong?

605
00:59:29,167 --> 00:59:34,036
He couldn't repay so I kept the house.

606
00:59:34,238 --> 00:59:39,039
You gave him the money
knowing fully well he'd...

607
00:59:39,243 --> 00:59:40,505
...never be able to repay.

608
00:59:40,712 --> 00:59:43,943
It's business.
And I'm a businessman.

609
00:59:44,148 --> 00:59:49,051
A very bad one.
Such a profitless deal.

610
00:59:49,253 --> 00:59:51,414
Why? What's the price?

611
00:59:51,622 --> 00:59:56,423
It's free... but too expensive for you.

612
00:59:57,362 --> 00:59:58,693
You've got everything.

613
00:59:59,097 --> 01:00:04,228
...an empire, fame...
and now this house too.

614
01:00:05,336 --> 01:00:07,964
But nobody is poorer than you today...

615
01:00:09,374 --> 01:00:11,239
...because you got the house...

616
01:00:14,345 --> 01:00:15,437
...but you've lost your son.

617
01:00:15,646 --> 01:00:19,550
You've gone mad.
You're going to be wed in a while.

618
01:00:19,550 --> 01:00:20,482
Mr. Tantiya is expecting us...

619
01:00:20,618 --> 01:00:26,147
...Ask him... will he wed his
daughter to a married man?

620
01:00:26,357 --> 01:00:27,654
What? - Yes.

621
01:00:28,926 --> 01:00:30,416
I'm already married.

622
01:00:30,762 --> 01:00:31,524
To whom?

623
01:00:32,764 --> 01:00:33,696
Lolita.

624
01:00:34,499 --> 01:00:36,865
Really, son? When?

625
01:00:38,169 --> 01:00:39,727
I don't consider it a marriage.

626
01:00:40,405 --> 01:00:42,270
Give her some money and...

627
01:00:42,473 --> 01:00:48,378
Enough. My wife is not for sale.

628
01:00:50,081 --> 01:00:55,678
Your mind is governed only
by money, isn't it, dad?

629
01:00:57,989 --> 01:00:59,422
And I feel sorry that

630
01:00:59,624 --> 01:01:02,320
I was following your path.

631
01:01:03,494 --> 01:01:04,825
You poisoned my mind so deeply;

632
01:01:04,996 --> 01:01:06,964
I saw everything through your eyes.

633
01:01:08,866 --> 01:01:15,066
I was reduced to business, deals,
money just like you...

634
01:01:17,141 --> 01:01:21,578
I even raised my hand on my wife.

635
01:01:22,847 --> 01:01:25,179
Stop it, son.

636
01:01:30,221 --> 01:01:31,245
Where are you going?

637
01:01:32,390 --> 01:01:37,828
To be a good husband
and bring my wife home.

638
01:01:38,529 --> 01:01:39,826
You won't go anywhere.

639
01:01:58,883 --> 01:02:00,214
Where are you going, son?

640
01:02:37,788 --> 01:02:38,812
What's overcome him?

641
01:02:39,023 --> 01:02:39,648
Shekhar.

642
01:02:49,367 --> 01:02:50,334
Shekhar.

643
01:02:52,537 --> 01:02:53,663
Shekhar.

644
01:02:57,008 --> 01:02:59,306
Break it, Shekhar.

645
01:03:00,778 --> 01:03:01,642
Break it.

646
01:03:02,480 --> 01:03:04,539
Ajit, stop him.

647
01:03:04,782 --> 01:03:13,850
Break it, Shekhar. Break it.
Break it, damn it.

648
01:03:14,692 --> 01:03:20,096
Break it, Shekhar. Break it.

649
01:03:46,624 --> 01:03:51,561
Stop watching the circus and
stop him. Call the police.

650
01:03:52,530 --> 01:04:02,906
Break it, Shekhar. Break it.

651
01:04:03,374 --> 01:04:05,899
What is this commotion?
- I'll check.

652
01:04:08,980 --> 01:04:10,174
Rajeshwari.

653
01:04:13,985 --> 01:04:20,049
Break it, son. Destroy it forever.

654
01:06:04,061 --> 01:06:11,229
Here, light these.
Light up the whole house.

655
01:06:11,469 --> 01:06:18,500
My daughter-in-law is home.

656
01:06:26,684 --> 01:06:29,118
Yes, tonight is Shekhar's wedding night.

657
01:06:30,087 --> 01:06:33,215
Just a few players have changed.

658
01:06:34,058 --> 01:06:36,618
And the city's dreams and
joys have returned.

659
01:06:36,827 --> 01:06:42,459
Calcutta is once again a city of joy.

